snippet.title: Rummel & Rabalder: Dr. Frank's Mask (FULL GAME)
snippet.description:
We're continuing the gameplay videos with a New game series! :D

Today we're playing the first "Rummel & Rabalder" game, Dr. Frank's Mask! ^^

This is a childhood game of mine as well like the Woodii games! I will play the next game of R&R so smash that Subscribe button so you don't miss out!! ENJOY!! :)
